  "title": "chore(typescript): setup TSLint (part 2)",
  "body": "This is the second step toward our process migrating to TypeScript.\r\n\r\n- **ESLint**.\r\n  - Resolve `js`, `ts` and `tsx` files.\r\n- **TSLint**.\r\n  - Add default configuration. This is the [same configuration as React InstantSearch](https://github.com/algolia/react-instantsearch/blob/93c5ce04bd6f26330dbaf77d2e9926ea98f59e96/tsconfig.json) plus the disabled rule `jsx-no-lambda` which we rely on heavily in the InstantSearch.js codebase.\r\n\r\n### Related\r\n\r\n- Part 1: #3411\r\n- Part 3: #3413\r\n- Part 4: #3414\r\n- Part 5: #3417",
